com.facebook.buck.cxx.toolchain.nativelink

Interface NativeLinkableGroup

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbstractCxxLibraryGroup
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CxxLibraryGroup, CxxPrecompiledHeaderTemplate, CxxPrefixHeader, DLibrary, HalideLibrary, HaskellLibrary, PrebuiltAppleFramework, PrebuiltCxxLibrary, PrebuiltHaskellLibrary, PreInclude, RustLibrary, SwiftRuntimeNativeLinkableGroup, SystemLuaCxxLibrary

    public interface NativeLinkableGroup
    Interface for BuildRule objects (e.g. C++ libraries) which can contribute to the top-level link of a native binary (e.g. C++ binary). This represents the linkable object for all platforms.
